---
title: Mozza-Roasted Red Pepper Turkey with Tomato-Zucchini Spaghetti
description: The best part of this Mozza Roasted Red Pepper Turkey is the layer of crispy cheese on top! Each bite is crispy, salty and cheesy. Served with tender Italian zucchini and perfectly cooked pasta, dinner tonight is simple and refined!
